  <summary date="2021-06-21T15:09:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Guard and Reserve Hazard Duty Pay Equity Act

This bill provides hazardous duty incentive pay to members of an Armed Forces reserve component or the National Guard who perform a parachute jump as an essential part of their military duty. Currently, only active duty members are entitled to hazardous duty incentive pay for performing such duties.</summary>
